Package nl.naturalis.nda.elasticsearch.load.nsr

Package that handles the import of the NSR data sources.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NsrBackupExtensionRemover
    Removes the .imported extension from XML files that have been successfully processed, so they will be picked up again by the NSR import programs.
    NsrImportAll
    Class that imports both taxa and multimedia from NSR.
    NsrImportUtil
    Class providing common functionality for NSR imports.
    NsrMultiMediaImporter
    Class that imports multimedia from NSR.
    NsrMultiMediaTransfer
    Transforms and validates NSR source data.
    NsrTaxonImporter
    Class that imports taxa from NSR.
    NsrTaxonTransfer
    Transforms and validates NSR source data.
